<!-- Game Cheats Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Twinbee Time Attack Full Power-up but timer at 9'59"99: Pause the game, then enter the standard Konami cheat code for a full power-up, but the timer will automatically be maxed out. -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;up, up , down, down, left, right, left, right, X, O</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Friendly (Nakayoshi) mode -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start a new game. Then at the screen where you choose your name or nickname, enter, "MI-NN-NA" ("everyone" in Hiragana) as your Myoji (family name). Then, enter "NA-KA-YO-SHI" ("friendly" in Kanji) as your Namae (first
name). Enter any value for a birth date, blood type, and other fields. All the female characters (except Ray) will be start in friendly status with your character. Ray is a female. Call her constantly on Sundays and holidays to have her fall in love with your character.</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Stardust Symphony Ex mini-game -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;This is a mini 3D shooter that demonstrates some of the PlayStation's 3D processing capabilities. It can be accessed by joining the Computer Programming Club for all 3 years and eventually becoming the Club Leader.</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Increase HPs during battles -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;During a battle, press Up(2), Down(2), Left, Right, Left, Right, X, Circle to increase HPs to 5730.</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Album mode -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;During the credits after the game ends, press Up(2), Down(2), Left, Right, Left, Right, X, Circle on controller two.</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Hidden karaoke songs -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Go on a date with any girl on March 3rd and take her out to the Karaoke bar. Then, quickly press Up(2), Down(2), Left, Right, Left, Right, X, Circle before entering the bar. Go inside and quickly press Up(2), Down(2), Left, Right, Left, Right, X, Circle at the screen that displays the selection of karaoke songs.</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Choosing karaoke songs -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Go to the Karaoke bar with any girl three times. On the fourth time, the message "Anata No Uta Mo, Kikitaina" will appear. Then, quickly press Up(2), Down(2), Left, Right, Left, Right, X, Circle.</font><br><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ACTION REPLAY CODES:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Main character Physical condition 999 -
       		<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;<br>800EE85E 03E7</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Main character Humanities 999 -
       		<font color="#00FF00"><br>800EE862 03E7</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Main character Science 999 -
       		<font color="#00FF00"><br>800EE866 03E7</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Main character Art 999 -
       		<font color="#00FF00"><br>800EE86A 03E7</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Main character Movement 999 -
       		<font color="#00FF00"><br>800EE86E 03E7</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Main character Trivia 999 -
       		<font color="#00FF00"><br>800EE872 03E7</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Main character Appearance 999 -
       		<font color="#00FF00"><br>800EE876 03E7</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Main character Guts 999 -
       		<font color="#00FF00"><br>800EE87A 03E7</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Main character Stress 0 -
       		<font color="#00FF00"><br>800EE87E 0000</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Bonus game all sub-selectable option -
       		<font color="#00FF00"><br>800F022E 0100<br>800F0230 0001</font>
			<br>&nbsp; Extra free talk all selectable options -
       		<font color="#00FF00"><br>800F0204 0101<br>800F0206 0101<br>800F0208 0101<br>800F020A 0101<br>800F020C 0101<br>800F020E 0101<br>800F0210 0101</font><br><br>			
                  &nbsp;</td>	 
